    "composer": "Capinam / Jards Macalé",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7(9)\">Dm7(9)</span>\n\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7(9)\">Dm7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7/5b\">Em7/5b</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(5+)\">A7(5+)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7(9)\">Dm7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Estou cansado             de você também</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7/Bb\">Dm7/Bb</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb6\">Bb6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Vou sair sem abrir a porta</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/4\">A7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E não voltar nunca mais</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">           Desculpe a paz que eu lhe roubei</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    E o futuro esperado que eu não dei</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7/Bb\">Dm7/Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    É impossível levar um barco sem temporais</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb6\">Bb6</span>                                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/4\">A7/4</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   E suportar a vida como um momento além do cais</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">           Que passa ao largo           do nosso corpo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">           Não quero ficar dando adeus</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    As coisas passando, eu quero</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    É passar com elas, eu quero</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    E não deixar nada mais</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Do que as cinzas de um cigarro</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb6\">Bb6</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/4\">A7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E a marca de um abraço no seu corpo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7/4\">D7/4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não,           não sou eu quem vai ficar no porto chorando, não</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Lamentando o eterno movimento</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/9\">C/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Movimento dos barcos, movimento</span>\n",
